Distribution . This species is known from Argentina , Bolivia and Paraguay (Walter Reed Biosystematics Unit 2001 ). It is recorded from the following provinces in Argentina : Buenos Aires, Chaco, Córdoba, Corrientes, Entre Ríos, Formosa , Salta, Santa Fe, Santiago del Estero (
Campos & Maciá 1998
), Mendoza (
Rossi et al . 2006
), La Rioja and Jujuy (
Visintin et al . 2009
).
